name: Open Standard Media Player
body: Introducing the Open Standard Media Player version 2.0!  This media player is an all-in-one media player for the web.  It is an industry changing, open source (GPL) media player that is built to dynamically deliver any type of web media, including HTML5, YouTube, Vimeo, and Flash.
